0">thee to turn away,&quot; caused the students </div><div class="t mf9 x27 he y1df ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thereof to turn from God. Verse 10, margin. </div><div class="t m1470 x26 he y2c7 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. What plea does God make to the </div><div class="t m858 x27 he y58f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">house of Jacob? What are they to do? </div><div class="t m6ac x27 he y327 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Isa. 48:17-20. </div><div class="t m351 x71 he y716 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.-The message in Isaiah 48 is di-</div><div class="t mb3 x27 he yc49 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rected to the house of Jacob, &quot;which are </div><div class="t m80e x15 he y5be ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">called by the name of Israel&quot; but &quot;not in </div><div class="t m341 x15 he y458 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth; nor in righteousness.&quot; Isaiah 48:1. </div><div class="t m44 x15 he y18b ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">That is, while they are called Israel, they </div><div class="t m5dc x15 he ye1f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are in reality only Jacobs, such as have not </div><div class="t m185a x4b he y34e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">NOTE.</div><div class="t m1e4a x3d h5f y34e ff4 fs13 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">-&quot;Isles,&quot; </div><div class="t m623 x67 he y1fa ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">literally, &quot;coastland,&quot; that </div><div class="t m37e x21 he y5e ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is, distant countries; &quot;people,&quot; literally, peo-</div><div class="t m281 x21 he y269 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ples. The whole world is called upon to hear </div><div class="t m1377 x21 he y1a3 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the announcement, for it concerns the whole </div><div class="t m1105 x21 he y49a ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">world. </div><div class="t m53 x86 he y1f ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The Lord hath called Me.&quot; See Luke </div><div class="t m7ec xbc he y2c2 ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1:31-33. </div><div class="t m9b8 x86 he y87d ff4 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Mention of My name.&quot; See 